Allen & Gledihll advised the joint issue managers in connection with Emperador Inc. listing. 
Emperador Inc. (PSE: EMI) announced its secondary listing on the Singapore Exchange. 
J.P. Morgan (S.E.A.) Limited and UBS AG, Singapore Branch acted as joint issue managers.
Emperador is a leading global integrated manufacturer, bottler and distributor of brandy, Scotch whisky and other alcoholic beverages, with a market capitalisation of approximately US$5.2 billion as of 20 June 2022, and whose shares are primary listed on the First Board of the Philippine Stock Exchange, Inc..
The Allen & Gledhill team included Partners Tan Tze Gay (Picture) and Rhys Goh and Counsel Kern Wong.
